{"tid":2195113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"影》印度稱60解放軍拿關刀棍棒與矛進逼 還鳴十幾槍威脅","createTime":"2020-09-09T03:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T03:46:25.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0e272324e1024bc141776064cc02054b5c2924","tid":2195113,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"在中印互控對方越界挑釁鳴槍，雙方緊張持續升高之際，印度政府消息人士周二說，周一晚有50-60名解放軍持棍棒，矛與關刀進逼印度在東拉達克熱藏拉（Rezang La）和穆赫帕里（Mukhpari）的陣地，並鳴槍威脅。<br />\n<br />\n據《印度時報》（The Times of India）等印度媒體8日報導，消息人士說，解放軍是要將印軍逐出拉達克穆赫帕里峰和熱藏拉山脊等戰略要地。他們說，解放軍周一約晚上6點時，逼近印軍在班公湖（Pangong Lake）南岸的哨站，但印方強烈對抗，而中方則鳴了約10-15槍威脅。這些消息人士強調，印軍並沒有動用任何槍枝。他們說，印度仍保有班公湖南岸附近的戰略高地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/umt1c5gG2MM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fumt1c5gG2MM&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=5fe9178a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/umt1c5gG2MM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZeVCaP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZeVCaP.jpg&h=679ab36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手持關刀棍棒的解放軍"},{"pid":"fa87aafeb1111d86799ebdeaa957e3032f0db66c","tid":2195113,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"華文傳媒唔識分「薙刀」同「關刀」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3NLYxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3NLYxj.jpg&h=e79acb9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73847d4176c9c3d99cbaf85eef518cad203dc9c5","tid":2195113,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"call of duty: Ancient Weapons"},{"pid":"83957d219257ccc0038ad055b30165c2c323f3dd","tid":2195113,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"屌你原來冷戰係用冷兵器咁解，全世界都誤會曬"},{"pid":"a599ff4a6c246c3e66f6a8d240171d456e1dc721","tid":2195113,"uid":28997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"